{"tid":791751,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"維達爾：歐聯有VAR技術 皇馬會少兩個冠軍","createTime":"2018-08-24T04:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T16:19:16.000Z","uid":147522,"like":69,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"d68589c3a2a11c7f816fbc16dc7e1fecaab4d21c","tid":791751,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T04:58:41.000Z","msg":"　　在接受《世界體育報》的專訪，巴塞新援維達爾向皇馬開炮，他認為如果有VAR技術，那麼拜仁能多拿兩個歐聯冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n　　維達爾說：「我最喜歡的冠軍就是歐聯。我知道巴塞曾經贏得過歐聯冠軍，但是我想現在就能獲得&mdash;&mdash;我想贏得全部的冠軍。如果有VAR技術，皇馬可能少拿兩個歐聯，拜仁可能多拿兩個歐聯冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n　　今年夏天因為保連奴的離隊，巴塞為了加強中場的實力，引進了智利中場維達爾。"},{"pid":"50369d14e8346daf1383c0700e1563340354218d","tid":791751,"uid":13343,"like":3,"dislike":31,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:04:14.000Z","msg":"山狗： 我想在曼聯贏盡冠軍<br />\n<br />\n去年曼聯冠軍數量：？？？？？？？<br />\n<br />\n恭喜疤塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ebab9a02b1c60f679710db32d94e4143609eb5","tid":791751,"uid":22054,"like":34,"dislike":3,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:04:48.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢咁君子緊係專燈炒左插水返黎既十二碼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c99b829badbdf90e75e80ad20fe0bb3f9de80b59","tid":791751,"uid":4308,"like":38,"dislike":4,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:13:27.000Z","msg":"佢自己夠係個不死人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231f7a32fce62946213636056532530b76393f02","tid":791751,"uid":10338,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:17:23.000Z","msg":"笑撚左啦<br />\n對祖記<br />\n黑鳩莫拉達個入球"},{"pid":"ce5b72312b700be8e28fd98565e633126795d912","tid":791751,"uid":10757,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"由疤講依d說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e5102eaf566bef3d96b5f110a0aa